'''陈浩亮'''（{{bd|1933年|5月5日|catIdx=Tan Howe Liang}}）出生於[[汕頭|汕頭]]，[[新加坡|新加坡]][[举重|举重]]运动员，也是2008年[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会|北京奧運會]]之前唯一为新加坡夺得奥运会奖牌的运动员<ref>{{cite web|url=https://olympics.com/en/news/weightlifter-tan-beats-pain-barrier-for-singapore-s-first-medal|title=Weightlifter Tan beats pain barrier for Singapore's first medal|publisher=Olympics.com|access-date=2021-09-07|archive-date=2021-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210907100329/https://olympics.com/en/news/weightlifter-tan-beats-pain-barrier-for-singapore-s-first-medal|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1960年9月9日，陈浩亮于[[罗马|罗马]][[1960年夏季奥林匹克运动会|夏季奥林匹克运动会]]上，以380公斤总成绩夺得男子[[举重|举重]]67.5公斤级银牌<ref>{{cite web|url=https://olympics.com/en/news/weightlifter-tan-beats-pain-barrier-for-singapore-s-first-medal|title=The Tiger who became a gladiator in Rome|publisher=Singapore National Olympic Council|date=2020-09-08|author=Justin Kor|access-date=2021-09-07|archive-date=2021-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210907100329/https://olympics.com/en/news/weightlifter-tan-beats-pain-barrier-for-singapore-s-first-medal|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

